wikipedia_page.main: Gary Whittaker (born 16 August 1974) is a Caymanian footballer who played as a forward. He represented the Cayman Islands in World Cup qualifying matches in 1996.Whittaker started his career at senior level as a 12-year-old and played club football for various Caymanian clubs including George Town SC, FC International (George Town), Academy SC and Cayman Athletic SC.
